
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-zhao-aalsec-access-00.txt'>
    <title>"AAL security in Low Power and Lossy Networks", Wei-Cheng Zhao</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-zhao-aalsec-access-00.txt</link>
    <description>Due to the seriously resource-constrained and easily attacked character of Low Power and Lossy Networks-LNs, security becomes even harder to be deployed. Here we present an AAL security scheme to protect devices in AAL layer to help protect to communicate with each other safely including a special key management, encryption, authentication and other security measures.</description>
    <dc:date>2014-11-18T08:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
